<h2>Stockholm Review of Latin American Studies 8 (2012) (Zeitschriftenheft)</h2>
<h3>Themenheft: &quot;¿Lenguas independientes? Sobre el lenguaje como un proceso dinámico: Independent languages? About language as a dynamic process&quot;</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1600'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
